theme_set(theme_roboto())
# These fonts must be installed locally on your computer for this theme to work: https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Roboto+Condensed and https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Roboto. 
mares = mares_nt %>% 
    mutate(Dia = ifelse(Dia == "", NA,   substr(Dia, 4, 15))) %>% 
    fill(Dia) %>% 
    transmute(Horario = dmy_hm(paste(Dia, Hora)), Mar = `Alt. (m)`)

unknown timezone 'zone/tz/2017c.1.0/zoneinfo/America/Recife'Error in mutate_impl(.data, dots) : Binding not found: Alt. (m).
mares %>% 
    group_by(Dia = day(`Horario`)) %>% 
    summarise(Mnima = min(`Mar`), Mxima = max(`Mar`)) %>% 
    ggplot(aes(x = Dia, ymin = `Mnima`, ymax = `Mxima`)) + 
    geom_ribbon(fill = "#FFA69E", color = "#462255", alpha = .8) + 
    geom_vline(aes(xintercept = day(now())), size = 3, alpha = .5, color = "#462255") + 
    annotate("text", x = day(now()), y = -.5, label = "Hoje", hjust = -.2 ) +
    labs(title = "Mxima e mnima por dia", 
         subtitle = "mar mais alta e mais baixa para cada dia do ms", 
         y = "Mars no dia", 
         x = "Dia do ms")
ggsave("mares-por-dia.png", width = 8, height = 5)

praia = tibble(Hora = c(8, 18), 
               `Mar_min` = min(mares$Mar), 
               `Mar_max` = max(mares$Mar))
    
mares %>% 
    mutate(Dia = day(Horario), Hora = hour(Horario)) %>% 
    ggplot() + 
    geom_ribbon(data = praia, aes(x = Hora, 
                                  ymin = `Mar_min`, 
                                  ymax = `Mar_max`), 
                fill = "yellow", 
                alpha = .5) +
    geom_area(aes(x = Hora, y = `Mar`), fill = "#93E1D8", color = "darkblue", alpha = .8) +
    facet_wrap(~ Dia) +
    labs(title = "Mar por horrio", 
         subtitle = "e por dia. o amarelo destaca das 8 s 18", 
         y = "Mar", 
         x = "Hora")
ggsave("mares-por-hora.png", width = 5, height = 6)
